  <brief_title>Non-Interventional Study of NovoSeven® Used in Patients With Haemophilia A and B With Inhibitors When Undergoing Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non-Interventional Study of NovoSeven® Used in Patients With Haemophilia A and B With Inhibitors When Undergoing Surgery</official_title>
