  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Japan. The aim of this non-interventional study is to investigate
      the safety and effectiveness of treatment with eptacog alpha (NovoSeven®) when undergoing
      surgery under normal clinical practice conditions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
